<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	#parse("comm/head.vm")
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>公司信息</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="#springUrl('/resource/css/pchongbao/webCompanyInfo.css')">
	<script src="#springUrl('/resource/js/pchongbao/webCompanyInfo.js')"></script>
	<script src="#springUrl('/resource/js/hongbao/ajaxfileupload.js')"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="companyHeader">
		<div class="logo">
			<img  src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/web-logo1.png')" />
		</div>
		<div class="logo-text">
			<img   src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/web-text1.png')"/>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="companyMain">
		<div class="companyMain-title">公司信息</div>
		<form id="companyForm">
			<!-- 隐藏域-->
            <input type="hidden" name="companyId" value="$!{companyId}"/>
			<input type="hidden" name="companyLogo" value="$!{companyLogo}"/>
			<input type="hidden" name="companyOrganizationImg" value="$!{companyOrganizationImg}" />
			<ul>
				<li class='companyName'>
					<label><em>*</em>公司名称</label>
					<input type="text" name="companyName"  value="$!{companyName}" placeholder="请输入公司名称（4-20位）"/>
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='companyLogo'>
					<label>公司LOGO</label>
					<div class="pic1">+
						#if($!{companyLogo}=="")
                            <img  src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/error.png')"  id="uploadLogo"/>
							#else
								<img src= "$!{companyLogoUrl}"  id="uploadLogo"/>
						#end
		                <input type="file"  name="file" id="companyLogoFile" />
					</div>
					<div class="logo1-hint">
						<p>请上传您公司的Logo</p>
						<p>支持jpg、jpeg、png、bmp格式照片，大小不超过5M</p>
					</div>
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='companyAddress'>
					<label><em>*</em>公司地址</label><input type="text"name="companyAddress" value="$!{companyAddress}" placeholder="请输入公司名称">
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='businessLicenseNumber'>
					<label><em>*</em>营业执照编号</label><input type="text" name="companyNumber" value="$!{companyNumber}" placeholder="请输入营业执照编号">
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='businessLicensePic'>
					<label><em>*</em>营业执照扫描件</label>
					<div class="pic2">+
						#if($!{companyOrganizationImg}=="")
                            <img  src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/error.png')"   id="uploadOrgImage"/>
							#else
                                <img src= "$!{companyOrganizationImgUrl}"  id="uploadOrgImage"/>
						#end
		                <input type="file"  name="file" id="companyOrganizationImgFile"/>

					</div>
					<div class="logo2-hint">
						<p>请上传带有公章的营业执照数码照，营业执照须在有效期内且年检齐全（当年成立可无年检）。</p>
						<p>支持.jpg.jpeg.png.bmp格式照片，大小不超过5M </p>
					</div>
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='legalPerson'>
					<label>法人代表</label><input type="text" name="companyCorporation" value="$!{companyCorporation}"  placeholder="输入法人代表（不多于20位）">
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='legalPhone'>
					<label><em>*</em>联系电话</label><input type="text" name="companyCorporationPhone" value="$!{companyCorporationPhone}"  placeholder="输入联系电话">
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='companyScale pull'>
					<label>公司规模</label><input type="text" name="companyScale" id="companyScale"  placeholder="请选择公司规模" readonly="readonly"/>
					<div class="list1 list" style="display: none">
						<p>50人以下</p>
						<p>50~100人</p>
						<p>100~200人</p>
						<p>200~500人</p>
						<p>500人以上</p>
					</div>
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class="industry pull"> 
					<label>所属行业</label><input type="text" name="companyBelongIndustry"  id="companyBelongIndustry"  placeholder="请选择所属行业！"/>
					<div class="list2 list" style="display: none">
						<p>互联网/游戏/软件</p>
						<p>电子/通信/硬件</p>
						<p>房地产/建筑/物业</p>
						<p>金融</p>
						<p>消费品</p>
						<p>汽车/机械/制造</p>
						<p>服务/外包/中介</p>
						<p>广告/传媒/教育/文化</p>
						<p>交通/贸易/物理</p>
						<p>广告/传媒/教育/文化</p>
					</div>
					<b></b>
				</li>
				<li class='ditch pull'>
					<label><em>*</em>了解薪太软的渠道</label><input type="text"  id="companyChannel"  value="$!{companyChannelOther}" name="companyChannelOther" placeholder="请选择您了解薪太软的渠道！"/>
					<input name="companyChannel"  value="$!{companyChannel}" type="hidden"/>
					<div class="list3 list " style="display: none">
						<p index="1">百度360，等搜索引擎</p>
						<p index="2">微信，QQ等社交平台</p>
						<p index="3">推销</p>
						<p index="4">广告</p>
						<p index="5">朋友介绍</p>
						<p index="6">其他</p>
					</div>
					<b></b>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</form>
		<!-- 提示 -->
		<div class="prompt1">
			<img   src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/prompt1.png')" />
		</div>
		<div class="prompt2">
			<img src="#springUrl('/resource/img/pchongbao/prompt2.png')" />
		</div>
	</div>	
	<div class="companyFooter">
			<input type="button" name="" class='companyClose' value="取消">
			<input type="button" name="" class='companyBtn' value="完成">
	</div>
</body>
<script type="text/javascript">
	
</script>
</html>